====================================================================================================================================
														Tasks Set

Task Set :
	- list of tasks.

														End Tasks Set
====================================================================================================================================
====================================================================================================================================
															Tasks 
Aperiodic tasks : ?

Periodic tasks : 
	- wcet
	- period
	- options :
		- offset
		- name
		- deadline (implicit deadline if absent)

Sporadic tasks : 
	- wcet
	- minimum inter arrival time
	- options :
		- offset
		- name
		- deadline (implicit deadline if absent)
		- distribution

MultiFrame tasks : 
	- period
	- list of wcet
	- options : 
	 	- offset
	 	- name
	 	- deadline (implicit deadline if absent)

Generalized multiframe tasks :
	- list of periods
	- list of wcet
	- options :
		- offset
		- name
		- list of deadlines (implicit deadlines if absent)

Non-cyclic GMF :
	- liste of periods
	- list of wcet
	- list of deadlines
	- options :
		- offset
		- name


DAG / RTT / Non-cyclic RTT / DRT / EDRT: 
	- Graph
	- Options : 
		- offset
		- name
Le type de graph change. Check le graph donné par rapport au type.
Représentation du graph : 
Graph :
	- Noeud :
		- id
		- wcet
		- deadline
	- Link :
		- source
		- dest
		- period
	- Options for EDRT :
		- inter-release separation constraint :
			- source
			- dest
			- time

Task Automaton : 
	- Graph
	- Options :
		- offset
		- name
Graph : 
	- Noeud : 
		- id 
		- wcet
		- deadline
	- Conditionnal link :
		- destination
		- source
		- clock name
		- comparison (>= || <= || > || < to a number)
	- Reset link :
		- destination
		- source
		- clock name
															End task
